flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Binding constraint detected affecting multi-plant fulfillment or a supplier shortage/commitment change that threatens demand fulfilment or materially increases COGS.]
  A --> N1[Stream: Process Builder - Stream (DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS) - Ingest enterprise and supplier signals]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast + RCA Service (via Process Builder - Data View) - Detect binding constraints and forecast impact]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder - Rules + Remote Functions (scenario simulation & cost calculus) - Generate and score mitigation scenarios}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Process Builder - Action Item + Remote Functions (API writeback to SAP S/4HANA) - Execute chosen plan or create CWB for exceptions]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle (Action Item / UI Screen) - Human review for high-risk or no-feasible options]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder - Notification + UI Screen (dashboard) - Surface results and notify stakeholders]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced incremental COGS from constraint-driven actions, improved on-time delivery, fewer stockouts, measurable P&L improvement (reduced expedite costs, lowered lost sales), and auditable execution trail for decisions and writebacks.]
  N3 -->|No feasible mitigation without violat...| B1[Escalate to CWB Lifecycle for executive review and negotiate supplier commitments or customer reprioritization]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Formal exception approved/rejected with documented rationale; temporary service concessions or demand reallocation executed]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Best-cost scenario requires supplier ...| B2[Fallback to alternate supplier sourcing scenario or internal overtime scenario simulated by Remote Functions and re-ranked by Rules]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Alternate plan executed (alternate supplier or internal schedule shift) with updated COGS impact and notifications]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Proposed schedule change materially i...| B3[Automatically create trade-off report and route to S&OP owner via CWB for approval before writeback]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Human approval preserves P&L guardrails; approved changes written back or plan rolled back if rejected]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]